r />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T11:22:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FPIkP89bKd0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFPIkP89bKd0&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyXjBGfL1Jh2LWroBhk3D7pk%3D&h=8e1f1204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FPIkP89bKd0</a>"},{"pid":"46989ac16fe2f849bf5f3217143399717457bb07","tid":2011996,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b50c05d2d58e6a8b78ae82c2429568f3bf7d43e4","tid":2011996,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T11:16:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200511/IQXQI5YAOZZBQU3JLKYLMQNLYM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200511%2FIQXQI5YAOZZBQU3JLKYLMQNLYM%2F&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyXjBGfL1Jh2LWroBhk3D7pk%3D&h=55076694\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200511%2FIQXQI5YAOZZBQU3JLKYLMQNLYM%2F&h=ff7c8a49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200511/IQXQI5YAOZZBQU3JLKYLMQNLYM/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">支那武漢肺炎</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EZdB8gg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEZdB8gg.gif&h=f6db8d01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIt's fact! <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T11:22:54.000Z","msg":"「中華民國」成中國學生課堂禁語？中原大學再聲明：從未禁止<br />\nNewTalk 2020/05/11 15:27(3小時前)<br />\n中原大學副教授招名威因於課堂上提及「武漢肺炎」、「中華民國台灣」等字眼，遭中原大學要求向中國學生道歉。   圖：翻攝自GOOGLE MAP<br />\n<br />\n新頭殼newtalk<br />\n<br />\n中原大學生物科技系副教授招名威日前在課堂上提及「武漢肺炎」、「中華民國台灣」等字眼，不料，竟引發中國學生不滿，向校方投訴，校方也立即要求招名威在課堂上公開道歉，引發爭議。中原大學上午先發出三點聲明，強調任何老師在課堂上若有非專業或與課程無關之言論，基於保障學生學習的立場，均會要求改進並加強輔導，但仍難熄輿論怒火，下午又再度發出聲明，宣稱校方從未禁止老師在課堂上提及中華民國。<br />\n<br />\n是否禁止教師在有中國學生的課堂提及「武漢肺炎」、「中華民國台灣」？中原大學下午再度發出聲明，強調中原大學為中華民國之大學，所聘任之老師皆受中華民國之保障，校方從未禁止老師在課堂上提及中華民國。中原大學一向以營造友善校園為教育使命，保障任何國家或地區學生的受教權，強調彼此尊重。任何老師在課堂上，學生若有反應教學意見，該校基於保障學生學習的立場，均會要求改善並加強輔導。此次行政單位在處理過程中，若有用語不夠精準之處，校方亦將要求改進。<br />\n<br />\n中原大學解釋，本案源自3月13日招老師「生物化學課」上課內容，經中原大學課程調查小組檢視上課影片及詢問當事人，證明招老師確實在上課時講述內容與課程專業無關，並建請改善。處理過程中，學校行政單位若有用語不夠精準之處，校方亦將要求改進。"},{"pid":"3afda833a0f6a632944d51235aa9d5de0a4c3daa","tid":2011996,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"162beaba09833dc4573a83316aaee7c92a3d77a2","tid":2011996,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b50c05d2d58e6a8b78ae82c2429568f3bf7d43e4","tid":2011996,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T11:16:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200511/IQXQI5YAOZZBQU3JLKYLMQNLYM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200511%2FIQXQI5YAOZZBQU3JLKYLMQNLYM%2F&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyXjBGfL1Jh2LWroBhk3D7pk%3D&h=55076694\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200511%2FIQXQI5YAOZZBQU3JLKYLMQNLYM%2F&h=ff7c8a49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200511/IQXQI5YAOZZBQU3JLKYLMQNLYM/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">支那武漢肺炎</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EZdB8gg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEZdB8gg.gif&h=f6db8d01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIt's fact! <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T11:22:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FPIkP89bKd0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFPIkP89bKd0&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyXjBGfL1Jh2LWroBhk3D7pk%3D&h=8e1f1204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FPIkP89bKd0</a>"},"citedBy":1,"r